data.description: Absolutely fantastic full ranch, one level living in Preserves in Perry Ga ! More than meticulously maintained! 4 sided brick, well built home in 2022 that features large great room with a nice beautiful isand, back splash in the kitchen and updated lighting throughout the home, granite counter tops,SS appliances. In the Master Shower is tiled with a garden tub. Enjoy pulling up to your new home and sitting on the front porch with a cup of coffee, bringining in FALL. You would not want to miss ths beautiful home. So call your agent to schedule a showing today, Respectfully....
